race.description: The Drive Home With Lu & Jarch Handicap
race.comment: COZZIES CHOICE (6) hasn't been far away in this grade in her past couple, finishing 1.5L off the winner last start at York. This shapes nicely for her once again with the claim of Cooper coming in handy. Maps to get every possible and she can return to the winner's list today. STORM LORD (3) beat home COZZIES CHOICE last start at York when running over the top to score by 0.4L as the race favourite. While he's likely to get well back from the draw, he showed that was no issue last time out. Can repeat the dose. PACIFIC BOXER (1) was strong first-up in a better race than this at Toodyay before a disappointing effort at Belmont last time out. He was sent back to the trials where he moved well and drops right back in grade today. Can turn his form around. ELSA'S PRIDE (5) is third-up now and can improve. SHORT STRAW (8) is next best off a couple of close maiden defeats recently.
